    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "This tightly sealed metal container is filled with highly pressurized gas that can explode to release a powerful shockwave. A pressure bomb deals the listed bludgeoning damage and splash damage. On a critical hit, the target is knocked prone. Many types grant an item bonus to attack rolls, and more powerful pressure bombs can knock creatures back.",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
          "alternate_type": "legacy",
          "aonid": 159,
          "game-obj": "Traits",
          "type": "alternate_link"
        },
        "classes": [
          "uncommon"
        ],
        "edition": "remastered",
        "game-id": "f31704572455b8d77a8bd97c0045fde6",
        "game-obj": "Traits",
        "links": [
          {
            "alt": "Recall Knowledge",
            "aonid": 26,
            "game-obj": "Actions",
            "name": "Recall Knowledge",
            "type": "link"
          }
        ],
        "name": "Uncommon",
        "sources": [
          {
            "errata": {
              "alt": "2.0",
              "aonid": 216,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "2.0",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "link": {
              "alt": "Player Core pg. 11",
              "aonid": 216,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "Player Core pg. 11",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "name": "Player Core",
            "page": 11,
            "type": "source"
          }
        ],
        "text": "Something of uncommon rarity requires special training or comes from a particular culture or part of the world. Some character choices give access to uncommon options, and the GM can choose to allow access for anyone. Less is known about uncommon creatures than common creatures. They typically can't be summoned. The DC of Recall Knowledge checks related to these creature is increased by 2.",
        "type": "trait"
      },
      {
        "alternate_link": {
          "alternate_type": "legacy",
          "aonid": 6,
          "game-obj": "Traits",
          "type": "alternate_link"
        },
        "classes": [
          "trait"
        ],
        "edition": "remastered",
        "game-id": "9fde9d3adae06c502c6263570964463e",
        "game-obj": "Traits",
        "links": [
          {
            "alt": "magical",
            "aonid": 644,
            "game-obj": "Traits",
            "name": "magical",
            "type": "link"
          }
        ],
        "name": "Alchemical",
        "sources": [
          {
            "errata": {
              "alt": "2.0",
              "aonid": 216,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "2.0",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "link": {
              "alt": "Player Core pg. 452",
              "aonid": 216,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "Player Core pg. 452",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "name": "Player Core",
            "page": 452,
            "type": "source"
          }
        ],
        "text": "Alchemical items are powered by reactions of alchemical reagents. Unless otherwise noted, alchemical items aren\u2019t magical and don\u2019t radiate a magical aura.  \n  \nAlchemical creatures are partially powered by alchemical reactions.",
        "type": "trait"
      },
      {
        "alternate_link": {
          "alternate_type": "legacy",
          "aonid": 21,
          "game-obj": "Traits",
          "type": "alternate_link"
        },
        "classes": [
          "trait"
        ],
        "edition": "remastered",
        "game-id": "e5bbf09ab73401e1f1ef8cd208e061d9",
        "game-obj": "Traits",
        "name": "Bomb",
        "sources": [
          {
            "errata": {
              "alt": "2.0",
              "aonid": 216,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "2.0",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "link": {
              "alt": "Player Core pg. 453",
              "aonid": 216,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "Player Core pg. 453",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "name": "Player Core",
            "page": 453,
            "type": "source"
          }
        ],
        "text": "An alchemical bomb combines volatile alchemical components that explode when the bomb hits a creature or object. Most alchemical bombs deal damage, though some produce other effects.",
        "type": "trait"
      },
      {
        "alternate_link": {
          "alternate_type": "legacy",
          "aonid": 36,
          "game-obj": "Traits",
          "type": "alternate_link"
        },
        "classes": [
          "trait"
        ],
        "edition": "remastered",
        "game-id": "07336d377bbfcf8d760f34f32f513526",
        "game-obj": "Traits",
        "name": "Consumable",
        "sources": [
          {
            "errata": {
              "alt": "2.0",
              "aonid": 216,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "2.0",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "link": {
              "alt": "Player Core pg. 454",
              "aonid": 216,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "Player Core pg. 454",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "name": "Player Core",
            "page": 454,
            "type": "source"
          }
        ],
        "text": "An item with this trait can be used only once. Unless stated otherwise, it\u2019s destroyed after activation. Consumable items include alchemical items and magical consumables such as scrolls and talismans. A character can Craft consumable items in batches of four.",
        "type": "trait"
      },
      {
        "alternate_link": {
          "alternate_type": "legacy",
          "aonid": 75,
          "game-obj": "Traits",
          "type": "alternate_link"
        },
        "classes": [
          "trait"
        ],
        "edition": "remastered",
        "game-id": "6a7f58e477505403e58cc11dfbae82ee",
        "game-obj": "Traits",
        "name": "Force",
        "sources": [
          {
            "errata": {
              "alt": "2.0",
              "aonid": 216,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "2.0",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "link": {
              "alt": "Player Core pg. 456",
              "aonid": 216,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "Player Core pg. 456",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "name": "Player Core",
            "page": 456,
            "type": "source"
          }
        ],
        "text": "Effects with this trait deal force damage or create objects made of pure magical force.",
        "type": "trait"
      },
      {
        "alternate_link": {
          "alternate_type": "legacy",
          "aonid": 150,
          "game-obj": "Traits",
          "type": "alternate_link"
        },
